24727221311812423098.Text: I heard that Archcanon Tholer Saryoni wishes to speak with me. I have been given a key to his quarters.

228357292870912744.Text: Tholer Saryoni told me that the First Corner of the House of Troubles is Malacath. There is a shrine to Malacath on the island of Sheogorad. To get there I should go south past the Dwemer ruins and take the second road heading west. I must find this shrine, donate four daedra hearts, and recite Vivec's "Four Corners."

20687099146495723.Text: I made the Pilgrimage to Dagon Fel and read a passage from the Four Corners of the House of Troubles.

306151332311623763.Text: Temple: Malacath of the House of Troubles
